title: $5500-4/3 Weston House-2 Car Garage-Pool-Custom Cabinets and Upgrades
posting_body: ['This gorgeous one-story 4 bedroom 3 bath home is located in the very desirable Lakes @ Weston.', 'The home feels open and bright with volume ceilings, wood laminate floors throughout and impact windows.', 'Large living room, formal dining room, family room and gourmet kitchen with Custom Kitchen Cabinets, Samsung Stainless Steel Appliances and Granite Counter tops.', "The owner's suite offers a large walk-in closet and a modern bath with a floating double-sink vanity and frame-less shower and soaking tub.", 'All three bathrooms have been updated this year.', 'Community has amazing amenities like the Soccer field, Playground and community Pool.', 'Walk to shopping, restaurants and houses of worship and only minutes to the highway.', '24hr guard gate.', 'A rated Weston schools.', 'No Association Approval necessary.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE – NOT SHORT TERM.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
